dc_title_s: Yamato zenkoku chizu Henshû nin Nakajima Kahê.
dc_description_s: In Japanese. Includes legend. Includes distance chart and list of local products. Relief shown by hachures. 1 map: col.; 101 x 70 cm., folded to 22 x 16 cm., in envelope 70 x 22 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
